  <body>
    <div class="content">
      <Sidebar selectedItem="home" />
      <nav class="main">
        <div class="container">
          <main class="fold-content-container">
            <div class="fold-content">
              <h1>Hi! I'm Toran.<br />I build things for the web.</h1>
              <p class="lead">
                Software Engineer focused on building optimised, user-friendly 
                interfaces for the web. Besides learning 
                new tools and tricks to improve my craft, I'm also a positive 
                team player, avid problem-solver, and proactive contributor 
