              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="">
              <a class="icon" href="mailto:toranbehera@gmail.com">
                <img src="/assets/email-svgrepo-com.svg" width="6%" alt="email_icon">
              </a>
              <a class="icon" href="https://github.com/toranbehera" target="_blank">
                <img src="/assets/GitHub_Invertocat_White.svg" width="6%" alt="github_icon">
